    <h3>3. Legal Obligations</h3>
    <p>We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid legal requests.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable measures to protect the data processed through our Service. However, no method of internet transmission is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
